#修改经度 https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44237337/article/details/119707332
lon_name = 'lon'  
ds['longitude_adjusted'] = xr.where(
    ds[lon_name] > 180,
    ds[lon_name] - 360,
    ds[lon_name])
ds = (
    ds
    .swap_dims({lon_name: 'longitude_adjusted'})
    .sel(**{'longitude_adjusted': sorted(ds.longitude_adjusted)})
    .drop(lon_name))
ds = ds.rename({'longitude_adjusted': lon_name})
ds

sst_anom_rolling = sst_anom.rolling(time=3, center=True).mean()#??what is the difference between rolling mean and running mean
# Plot 12-month rolling mean
sst_anom_rolling_line=sst_anom_rolling.mean(dim=['lat', 'lon'])#
sst_anom_rolling_line.plot(color='k',linewidth=1,label="3-month rolling mean")

plt.axhline(y=0.5, color='red', linestyle='--',linewidth=0.7,label='EI Nino Threshold')

plt.fill_between(sst_anom_rolling['time'], sst_anom_rolling_line, 0,
                 where=(sst_anom_rolling_line >0 ),
                 interpolate=True,color='red', alpha=0.3, )
plt.fill_between(sst_anom_rolling['time'], sst_anom_rolling_line, 0,
                 where=(sst_anom_rolling_line <=0 ),

        In [18]:
        fig, axes = plt.subplots(ncols=2, figsize=(18,5), dpi=300)

R = 6371393

toa_net_weighted = ds.toa_net_all_mon.weighted(weights).sum(dim='lon') *np.pi**2*R**2 /180/180 /1e14
toa_net_weighted = toa_net_weighted.rename('total amount $(10^{14}W)$')
toa_net_weighted.plot(ax=axes[0],x='time',cmap='plasma_r')
axes[0].set_title('net radiation in each 1-degree latitude band $(10^{14}W)$',fontsize=14)

toa_net_weighted2 = toa_net_weighted.sum(dim='time')
toa_net_weighted2 = toa_net_weighted2.rename('total amount $(10^{14}W)$')
toa_net_weighted2.plot(ax=axes[1],color='purple',linewidth=4)
axes[1].set_title('net radiation in each 1-degree latitude band $(10^{14}W)$',fontsize=14)
axes[1].set(xlim=(-90,90),ylim=(-600,800))
axes[1].set_xticks([-90,-60,-30,0,30,60,90])

ds_anom_rolling = SNOWDP_GL_anom.rolling(time=12, center=True).mean()
